embeds.title: Getting Support for AdvancedServerList
embeds.description:
To receive support, do the following:

1. Don't ask to ask, just ask your question/State your problem.
2. Be as detailed as possible when explaining the issue you have. Share screenshots if it helps you explain things better.
3. Provide the latest.log file from your server/proxy.
  - Do **not** share them directly as a file! Instead use a site such as https://mclo.gs or another paste site.
4. **Be patient.** Receiving support is a privilege, not a right. People here will answer if they can, but aren't required to.

While you wait, make sure to [check the documentation](https://asl.andre601.ch/) for anything that may answer your question/fix your problem.
